data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom, 2 bath plus office home in the Grand Phase 1 Addition in Noble. This roomy beauty boasts an open living floorplan, topped off with high ceilings, crown molding and a gas fireplace. Large open kitchen with custom wood work, tons of storage, large walk-in pantry, and an island with beautiful granite countertops. Oil-rubbed bronze fixtures throughout and much more. Covered patio, large backyard with privacy fence. Great for entertaining. Oversized lot, located on a cozy cul-de-sac!.
